I see a lot of people giving advice to people about depression and staying positive. Well sometimes it‚Äôs impossible to smile...impossible to laugh...to see or feel happiness...to find the good. 
We all have these feelings but there are some that can‚Äôt move forward and turn the page. So to say ‚Äústay positive‚Äù I feel is a little insensitive to those people that need professional help or the help from their friends and family. 
I‚Äôm sorry @sushantsinghrajput that your last option in this world was to take your own life. But I hope you found the happiness you deserve even though the ones you left behind will forever be sad you are no more.

God bless you and your family. RIP
